4. **Instrument Validity (Step 6):** Given the potential for instrument proliferation in System GMM, explicitly state that you will use the "Hansen J-test" specifically to check for the validity of the instruments, but also emphasize the "Difference-in-Hansen" test to specifically validate the additional moment conditions introduced by the System GMM (the level equations).

